channel.title: Client help
channel.description:
Hi, I was wondering, I use the testscape source and i can't get my servers i-p up, I have downloaded everything including no-ip... now what? I cant find the java file, everyone says to change ip, where can i find this?
Im using a D-link D-524 Router...
please help me with this, who ever can solve this problem will get 10 kudos and mod on server, or even admin.
please help.

item.title: Client help
item.dc:creator: @Mod_Baker Mod Baker
item.description:
@Mod_Baker wrote:

Tbh I cant under stand what you said so im just going to tell you what i told the other guy-
Get No-Ip, then make a account, after that click “click here to sign in to No-IP and create hosts.” at the very bottom, and follow the form.
Click the host to update then run your Runserver. Try loggoing in, and if it doesnt work then you 43594 port is not open.
